as the Indians (15-2, 4-0) preserved their unbeaten Foothill League record and 
defeated Burroughs for the first time in Coach Pam Walker's 4-year tenure at 
Hart. 
</P>
<P>
Maranatha 42, L.A. Baptist 35 -- Debbie Maccioli scored 15 and Debbie Miller 
added 12 as the Minutemen overcame a 4-point first quarter deficit to win an 
Alpha League game at Maranatha. 
</P>
