In the Sunset League: 
</P>
<P>
Fountain Valley 69, Marina 55 -- Stacey Hisaki scored 20 points to lead host 
Fountain Valley (13-7, 3-1). Melisa Sortino scored 27 points for Marina (15-5, 
3-1). 
</P>
<P>
Huntington Beach 60, Westminster 42 -- Jennifer Ambrose had 20 points and Janet 
Davis 16 for Huntington Beach (3-12, 1-3). at Westminster. 
</P>
